" easier search                     Easymotion
""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
nmap ,f <leader><leader>
nmap <leader><leader>. <Plug>(easymotion-repeat)
nmap <leader><leader>f, <Plug>(easymotion-overwin-f)
nmap <leader><leader>w, <Plug>(easymotion-overwin-w)

